      • SimpleVirtualMachine

        public SimpleVirtualMachine(String name,
                    int nbOfCPUs,
                    int cpuConsumption,
                    int memoryConsumption)
        New virtual machine with a given resource consumption. The current resource demand is set to the resource consumption.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the virtual machine
        nbOfCPUs - the number of virtual CPUs allocated to the virtual machine
        cpuConsumption - the current cpu consumption of the virtual machine
        memoryConsumption - the current memory consumption of the virtual machine
